{"tid":1847310,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"恐武漢肺炎疫情社區擴散　公僕明起5天留在家辦公","createTime":"2020-01-28T04:16:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T04:36:00.000Z","uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"76394577eb82febe0dbf7a226e65ab7815e6c53d","tid":1847310,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T04:16:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200128/photo/bkn-20200128113058527-0128_00822_001_01p.jpg?20200128115124\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200128%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200128113058527-0128_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20200128115124&h=8fd9f43a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">政府僱員在假期後毋須返回寫字樓辦公，而是留在家中工作。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n政府今日(28日)宣布，為盡量減低武漢肺炎疫情在社區擴散的風險，政府部門將會於農曆新年假期後，即明日(29日)起實施特別上班安排。除了提供緊急和必須公共服務的人員外，政府僱員在假期後毋須返回寫字樓辦公，而是留在家中工作。<br />\n<br />\n發言人表示，有關安排暫定實行至下月2日，政府屆時會再檢視情況，並呼籲私人機構在可行情況下作類似安排。政府個別政府部門稍後會就受影響的公共服務作出公布。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200128/mobile/bkn-20200128113058527-0128_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200128%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200128113058527-0128_00822_001.html&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtb6C2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=1cf2e723\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200128/mobile/bkn-20200128113058527-0128_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"590ca60124aca75163baeccb0d5b0c63882615e1","tid":1847310,"uid":40118,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76394577eb82febe0dbf7a226e65ab7815e6c53d","tid":1847310,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T04:16:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200128/photo/bkn-20200128113058527-0128_00822_001_01p.jpg?20200128115124\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200128%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200128113058527-012